.SH "EXAMPLES"
.IX Header "EXAMPLES"
Convert a paravirt guest from \f(CW\*(C`image.vmx\*(C'\fR:
.PP
.Vb 1
\&  # virt\-convert \-\-arch=i686 \-\-paravirt image.vmx
.Ve
.PP
